Phn tch v Khm ph d liu.

Tm cu tr li cho cc cu hi nghin cu:

  • Nhng c trng v t kha no mang tnh phn bit cao nht trong mt tin tuyn dng gi mo.

M t d liu:

  • Job_id : id ca cng vic
  • title : tiu ca bi bo tuyn dng
  • location : a ch ca cng ty - ni lm vic
  • department : v tr cng vic
  • salary_range : Khong lng
  • company_profile : profile ca cng ty
  • description : M t
  • requirements : yu cu ca cng vic
  • benefits : quyn li
  • telecommuting : c s lin lc hay khng
  • has_company_logo : cng ty c logo hay khng
  • has_questions : c cu hi hay khng
  • employment_type : kiu cng vic (full-time, part-time, other)
  • required_experience : yu cu kinh nghim
  • required_education : yu cu hc v
  • industry : lnh vc cng vic
  • function : vai tr cng vic
  • fraudulent : gian ln hay khng

In[]:
whilelist = []
for word in STOPWORDS:
    fake_mean = fake_text.str.count(fr'\b{re.escape(word)}\b').mean()
    real_mean = real_text.str.count(fr'\b{re.escape(word)}\b').mean()
    if fake_mean > real_mean:
        whilelist.append(word)
    else: continue

# --- 1. HM LM SCH (QUAN TRNG NHT) ---
def clean_text(text):
    if not isinstance(text, str):
        return ""
    
    # 1. Chuyn thnh ch thng
    text = text.lower()
    
    # 2. Loi b th HTML (v d: <br>, <div>, <li>)
    text = re.sub(r'<.*?>', ' ', text)
    
    # 3. Loi b k t c bit v s (ch gi li ch ci)
    # Nu mun gi s lng th sa thnh [^a-z0-9\s]
    text = re.sub(r'[^a-z\s]', '', text)
    
    # 4. Loi b khong trng tha
    text = re.sub(r'\s+', ' ', text).strip()
    
    return text

# --- 2. CHUN B D LIU ---
# m bo index chun
df = df.reset_index(drop=True)
df['fraudulent'] = pd.to_numeric(df['fraudulent'], errors='coerce').fillna(0).astype(int)

# Gp ct (Nu cha gp)
# df['combined_text'] = df['title'] + ' ' + df['description'] + ' ' + df['requirements']

# X l thiu
df['combined_text'] = df['combined_text'].fillna("").astype(str)

# P DNG HM LM SCH (y l bc bn b thiu)
print("ang lm sch d liu... (Vui lng i)")
df['combined_text'] = df['combined_text'].apply(clean_text)

# --- 3. TRCH XUT T KHA ---
if sum(df['fraudulent'] == 1) == 0:
    print(" LI: Khng c tin gi no trong d liu!")
else:
    # Cu hnh Vectorizer
    # - ngram_range=(1, 2): Ly c cm 2 t (v d: "data entry" s c ngha hn l "data" ng mt mnh)
    # - min_df=5: B qua cc t xut hin qu t (di 5 ln) -> Gim rc
    vec = CountVectorizer(stop_words='english', max_features=5000, ngram_range=(1, 2), min_df=5)
    
    X = vec.fit_transform(df['combined_text'])
    feature_names = vec.get_feature_names_out()

    # Tch nhm
    mask_fake = (df['fraudulent'] == 1).values
    mask_real = (df['fraudulent'] == 0).values
    
    fraud_counts = np.array(X[mask_fake].sum(axis=0)).flatten()
    real_counts = np.array(X[mask_real].sum(axis=0)).flatten()

    # Tnh ton
    total_fraud = fraud_counts.sum()
    total_real = real_counts.sum()
    
    df_freq = pd.DataFrame({
        'word': feature_names,
        'fraud_count': fraud_counts,
        'real_count': real_counts
    })
    
    # Chun ha tn sut ( so snh cng bng)
    df_freq['fraud_rate'] = (df_freq['fraud_count'] + 1) / (total_fraud + 1)
    df_freq['real_rate'] = (df_freq['real_count'] + 1) / (total_real + 1)
    
    # Tnh im s khc bit (Difference Score)
    # im cng cao -> Cng c trng cho Tin Gi
    df_freq['score'] = df_freq['fraud_rate'] / df_freq['real_rate']
    
    # Lc b t rc (nhng t ch xut hin vi ln  tin gi)
    df_freq = df_freq[df_freq['fraud_count'] > 10] 

    print("\n=== TOP 20 T KHA/CM T C TRNG CA TIN GI ===")
    print(df_freq.sort_values(by='score', ascending=False)[['word', 'fraud_count', 'real_count', 'score']].head(20))
